{"tid":718622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"隔離同事係個忽然球迷，今日忍唔住","createTime":"2018-06-26T22:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T02:21:39.000Z","uid":17628,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c97958be2c345bfa81e9b6a73ec78585a00b549","tid":718622,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T22:59:48.000Z","msg":"隔離同事係一個好鍾意認屎認屁嘅人，乜佢都扮識咁，當然世界盃到咗，佢都唔執輸，做忽然球迷<br />\n<br />\n同:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早兩日前<br />\n<br />\n同: 唉，尋晚啲friend約我出去睇波，三更半夜點出吖，雖然我好支持嗰兩隊<br />\n<br />\n我: 估唔到你係支持哥倫比亞同波蘭喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲以為你支持英格蘭添<br />\n<br />\n同: 英格蘭嗰啲邊夠西班牙嗰啲跑得快吖，根本唔夠踢，所以我唔會支持英格蘭，我唔係一味支持英格蘭㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我: 吓唔係田徑比賽喎，唔係鬥快㗎喎，況且西班牙係踢控球㗎喎<br />\n<br />\n同: 不過英格蘭嗰啲人都唔出名嘅<br />\n<br />\n我: 吓係咁又係，咁你今屆支持西班牙邊個球員呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同: 王子囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e34fd476ff32e64ba074b68f8a75c2624a59da1","tid":718622,"uid":18728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T23:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1746240100d02eba573bf65b503c72409403409e","tid":718622,"uid":62384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T23:23:29.000Z","msg":"支持西班牙海鮮炒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad317f82ebc7725112704f01678c1d54a2439ec3","tid":718622,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:20:10.000Z","msg":